{"tid":938582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海上自衛隊少校嫖未成年少女遭停職 30人受害","createTime":"2018-12-12T12:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T12:59:15.000Z","uid":212399,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"26f53aab15a2c6f73980faf350dcd1381271c32f","tid":938582,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2696/d2696992.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2696%2Fd2696992.jpg&h=76612920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海上自衛隊一名三等海佐因為跟未成年少女援交，遭停職12個。(示意圖／記者張一中攝)<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n日本「共同社」報導， 日本海上自衛隊周三(12日)以嫖未成年少女爲由，對「海上幕僚監部」人事教育部教育課所屬的一名三等海佐(海軍少校)給以停職12個月的處分。<br />\n據了解，這名海佐大約從8年前開始先後跟30名左右女中學生進行性交易(援交）。<br />\n據海上自衛隊消息指出，2017年6月時，這名30多歲的三等少佐在日本北九州市的一家酒店裡，在明知對方未成年的情況下猥亵一名女子。福岡縣警方在11月20日以涉嫌違反《禁止針對兒童的買春和色情法》， 将他的資料送交檢方。<br />\n「海上幕僚監部」廣報室室長戶井雄一郎表示：「這是讓人極其遺憾的行爲。我們将徹底做好自衛隊員的指導工作，盡全力防止這類情況再度發生。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181212/1329280.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181212%2F1329280.htm&d=0cDfHLXBfj5lCtx6NEeU%2B0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e30b9c4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181212/1329280.htm</a>"},{"pid":"01c0e169a83ab4304092d09136502a6f00878345","tid":938582,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817932e6f13634dc69f039d7224f50bbea5e5781","tid":938582,"uid":121546,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:09:48.000Z","msg":"標題係未成年少女,內文張圖係中年女人對腳"},{"pid":"53053758fdbfbb364e72d2cb133e99a7f09fa373","tid":938582,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"817932e6f13634dc69f039d7224f50bbea5e5781","tid":938582,"uid":121546,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:09:48.000Z","msg":"標題係未成年少女,內文張圖係中年女人對腳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"30中sales腳都可以咁"},{"pid":"76ae7913f5ce5365520c492d242c3406e77b19b0","tid":938582,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28387496412c12a9da9bcf6d0192158cfb221e9","tid":938582,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:47:08.000Z","msg":"海上自慰隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f701915c425b0932160256da4bf19dcfcdca45","tid":938582,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:49:46.000Z","msg":"幾多歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777bcfe736ac2c1062397bf7728d5ff1d2c96831","tid":938582,"uid":39316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:59:15.000Z","msg":"呢單新聞做乜會配幅充滿肌肉既中女腳圖"}]}